<p><strong>My name is Celia Adams, and I run a Chartered Accountancy practice in Worcestershire.</strong></p>
<p><img style="float: left;" alt="celia-adams-turnaround-director(1)" src="/images/stories/celia-adams-turnaround-director(1).png" width="124" height="141" /></p>
<p>I've carefully compiled the information within this website to provide a clear overview of the services I provide, and the manner with which I do so. I'm a strong believer in focusing on people before numbers, and I hope that comes across.</p>
<p>As a <a href="/experience">turnaround director</a>, I specialise in turning around failing businesses. I am also a <a href="/what-is-a-non-executive-director">non-executive director</a> and a <a href="/experience">business angel/investor</a>.</p>
<p>Over the years, I have worked with a whole range of interesting and exciting businesses, from corporates to charities to Non Departmental Public Bodies. More information on me is available on my <a href="/about-me">About Me</a> page, and real-world examples of businesses I have turned around can be found on my <a href="/experience">Experience page</a>.</p>
<p>If you do have any questions, please feel free to <a href="/contact-me">contact me</a>.</p>
<p>You can also connect with me on <a href="http://uk.linkedin.com/in/ceciliaadams">LinkedIn</a> and <a href="http://twitter.com/CeciliaAdams">Twitter</a>.</p>
<p> </p>
